      "output": "{\n  \"search_id\": \"search_b92a155f51df41f4957ff3b79170e78b\",\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/Device/HP_Omen_15-ax243dx\",\n      \"title\": \"HP Omen 15-ax243dx Repair Help: Learn How to Fix It Yourself.\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Free Shipping on Domestic Orders $75+\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx\\n\\nTable of Contents\\n\\n* Background\\n* Identification\\n* Additional Information\\n\\n* Edit\\n* Options\\n\\n* History\\n* \\n* Show Other Languages\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx Repairability: **7** / 10\\n\\nRepairability: **7** / 10\\n\\n# HP Omen 15-ax243dx Repair\\n\\nThe HP Omen 15-ax243dx is a light weight gaming notebook released in 2016.\\n\\nAuthor: vangnam (and 7 other contributors)\\n\\nCreate a Guide\\n\\nI Have This\\n\\n## Popular Forum Questions\\n\\nAsk a Question\\n\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### Spilled sugary soda on power supply adapter. What do I do?\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx |\\n| --- | --- |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### Battery discharging rapidly from 70% to 7%\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### Looking for where to source a specific component\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx |\\n|2 Answers\\n\\n0 Score |### Why showing something went wrong?\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx |\\n\\n## Documents\\n\\n## [Parts](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_Omen_15-ax243dx)\\n\\n* [Batteries (1)](https://www.ifixit.\\ncom/Parts/HP_Omen_15-ax243dx/Batteries)\\n\\n* [Case Components (1)](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_Omen_15-ax243dx/Case_Components)\\n\\n* [Keyboards (1)](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_Omen_15-ax243dx/Keyboards)\\n\\n## [Tools](https://www.ifixit.com/Tools)\\n\\nThese are some common tools used to work on this device. You might not need every tool for every procedure.\\n\\n## Background\\n\\nThe HP Omen 15 ax243dx is the first generation of the popular gaming laptop series from HP. It was released in 2016. The model number of the laptop is W2N35UA based on the manufacturer number.\\n\\nThe HP Omen 15 ax243dx came stocked with 1 TB of storage, 8 GB of RAM, a 2.8-GHz Intel Core i7-7700HQ processor. The main color of the device is black. The device is only 4.9 lbs which is considered to be a low-weight device compared to other gaming laptops. The screen resolution is 1920 x 1080 with a Diagonal FHD IPS UWVA anti-glare WLED-backlit.\\nHowever, this is not a competitive feature because most of the gaming laptops nowadays have the 4K display. With the Nvidia GeForce GTX 1050/Intel HD Graphics 630 embedded in the system, the HP Omen 15-ax243dx is capable of running smoothly in most of the high-quality video games such as Battlefield 1, Call of Duty World War II.\\n\\nThe HP Omen 15-ax243dx was replaced by the HP Omen X on August 22nd, 2017.\\n\\n## Identification\\n\\nThe HP Omen 15 ax243dx laptop can be identified by the model number printed on the label located on the bottom of the device. If the label has been removed, you can find the model number beneath the battery. For additional help identifying your device, visit the [HP Support page](https://support.hp.com/us-en/document/ish_2039298-1862169-16) .\\n\\n## Additional Information\\n\\n* [OMEN by HP 15-ax243dx Laptop PC Product Specifications](https://support.hp.com/ca-en/document/c05381485)\\n* [HP Omen 15-ax243dx Maintenance and Service guide](http://h10032.www1.hp.\\ncom/ctg/Manual/c04620176)\\n* [Comparasion between HP Omen 15-ax243dx with Lenovo and Mac](https://www.gadgetsnow.com/compare-laptops/HP-Omen-15-ax243dx-W2N35UA-Laptop-Core-i7-7th-Gen8-GB1-TB-128-GB-SSDWindows-104-GB-vs-Lenovo-Ideapad-Y700-80Q000E3IH-Laptop-Core-i7-6th-Gen16-GB1-TB-128-GB-SSDWindows-104-GB)\\n* [HP Omen 15-ax243dx on Amazon](https://www.amazon.com/HP-OMEN-15-6-i7-7700HQ-NVIDIA/dp/B01MTG5JYS?tag=ifixitam-20)\\n* [HP Omen 15-ax243dx Review with Specification](http://laptopmedia.com/review/hp-omen-15-gtx-1050-ti-review-beautiful-lightweight-and-compact-chassis-but-comes-at-a-price-and-a-couple-of-trade-offs/)\\n\\n### Author\\n\\nwith 7 other contributors\\n\\n#### vangnam\\n\\nMember since: 10/19/17\\n\\n599 Reputation\\n\\n4 Guides authored\\n\\nBadges: 14\\n\\n* \\n* \\n* \\n\\n\\\\+11 more badges\\n\\n### Team\\n\\n#### UMass Dartmouth, Team S6-G7, Rockett Fall 2017 Member of UMass Dartmouth, Team S6-G7, Rockett Fall 2017\\n\\nUMASSD-ROCKETT-F17S6G7\\n\\n3 Members\\n\\n7 Guides authored\\n\\n**View Statistics:**\\n\\nPast 24 Hours: 7\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/Device/HP_OMEN_15_Series\",\n      \"title\": \"HP OMEN 15 Series Help: Learn How to Fix It Yourself.\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Free Shipping on Domestic Orders $75+\\n\\nHP OMEN 15 Series\\n\\n* Edit\\n* Options\\n\\n* History\\n* \\n* Show Other Languages\\n\\nHP OMEN 15 Series\\n\\n# HP OMEN 15 Series\\n\\nRepair guides, manuals, and troubleshooting help for HP OMEN 15 Series. Get everything you need to repair your HP OMEN 15 Series yourself.\\n\\nAuthor: Matt Perona (and one other contributor)\\n\\nCreate a Guide\\n\\n## Popular Forum Questions\\n\\nAsk a Question\\n\\n|2 Answers\\n\\n1 Score |### Why won't my hp omen laptop not turn on?\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ax280nd |\\n| --- | --- |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n1 Score |### How to enable Advance bios in HP Omen 15 (2020)\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ek0000 Series |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n1 Score |### USB port on one side not working -RESOLVED\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ax280nd |\\n|3 Answers\\n\\n0 Score |### 5 longe 3 short Caps lock light IDK? OMEN Laptop - 15-dh1005na\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dh0000 Series |\\n\\n## [Parts](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_OMEN_15_Series)\\n\\n* [Batteries (7)](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_OMEN_15_Series/Batteries)\\n\\n* [Case Components (1)](https://www.ifixit.\\ncom/Parts/HP_OMEN_15_Series/Case_Components)\\n\\n* [Keyboards (2)](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_OMEN_15_Series/Keyboards)\\n\\n* [Ports (1)](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_OMEN_15_Series/Ports)\\n\\n### Author\\n\\nwith 1 other contributor\\n\\n#### Matt Perona\\n\\nMember since: 10/19/22\\n\\n26,545 Reputation\\n\\n0 Guides authored\\n\\nBadges: 16\\n\\n* \\n* \\n* \\n\\n\\\\+13 more badges\\n\\n### Team\\n\\n#### iFixit Member of iFixit\\n\\nStaff\\n\\n122 Members\\n\\n26,591 Guides authored\\n\\n**View Statistics:**\\n\\nPast 24 Hours: 6\\n\\nPast 7 Days: 82\\n\\nPast 30 Days: 307\\n\\nAll Time: 12,521\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/Device/HP_Omen\",\n      \"title\": \"HP OMEN Series Repair Help: Learn How to Fix It Yourself.\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Free Shipping on Domestic Orders $75+\\n\\nHP OMEN Series\\n\\n* Edit\\n* Options\\n\\n* History\\n* \\n* Show Other Languages\\n\\nHP OMEN Series\\n\\n# HP OMEN Series Repair\\n\\nRepair information for the HP OMEN laptop series.\\n\\nAuthor: Kyle Smith (and 3 other contributors)\\n\\nCreate a Guide\\n\\n## 6 Categories\\n\\nNew Page\\n\\nHP OMEN 15 Series ##### HP OMEN 15 Series\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ce198wm ##### HP OMEN 15-ce198wm\\n\\nHP OMEN 16 Series ##### HP OMEN 16 Series\\n\\nHP Omen 16 WD0017CI ##### HP Omen 16 WD0017CI\\n\\nHP OMEN 17 Series ##### HP OMEN 17 Series\\n\\nHP OMEN X Series ##### HP OMEN X Series\\n\\n## Popular Forum Questions\\n\\nAsk a Question\\n\\n|2 Answers\\n\\n1 Score |### Why won't my hp omen laptop not turn on?\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ax280nd |\\n| --- | --- |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n1 Score |### How to enable Advance bios in HP Omen 15 (2020)\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ek0000 Series |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n2 Score |### Keyboard Replacement for OMEN 16\\n\\nHP OMEN 16 Series |\\n|3 Answers\\n\\n0 Score |### 5 longe 3 short Caps lock light IDK? OMEN Laptop - 15-dh1005na\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dh0000 Series |\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://ifixit-guide-pdfs.s3.amazonaws.com/pdf/ifixit/guide_99368_en.pdf\",\n      \"title\": \"HP Omen 15-ax243dx Screen Replacement - ifixit-guide-pdfs.s3 ...\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Well you are in luck, if you follow our steps on how to disassembly the screen off the HP-Omen computer and reassembly the screen back on. This guides difficulty is moderate and contains 9 total steps that will take you approximately 20-40 minutes to complete it.\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/laptop-repairability-scores\",\n      \"title\": \"Laptop Repairability Scores | Most Repairable Laptops - iFixit\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"# Laptop Repairability Scores\\n\\nJump to Scores\\n\\n# You have the right to repair the things you own—but how easily can that be done?\\n\\nTo find out, our engineers tear down the latest laptops and score their repairability from zero (unrepairable) to ten (easiest to repair) so you can pick a product that is easy to repair and lasts as long as possible.\\n\\n# What makes a repairable device?\\n\\nIt should be straightforward to disassemble and replace whatever’s broken, using parts and instructions supplied (or endorsed) by the manufacturer. But that’s just to start—repairability means so much more. For full details, see our [repairability scoring explainer](https://www.ifixit.com/News/75533/how-ifixit-scores-repairability) .\\n\\n# Repairability is a moving target\\n\\nWe update our scoring rubric frequently to stay current with new technologies, materials, and design trends.\\nThis means that devices scored in years past might not fare exactly the same if they were re-scored today, but they can be readily compared with their contemporaries. For a precise list of criteria used to calculate each score, click the scorecard version number linked to each device below. For a downloadable (CSV) list of all scores, [click here](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1R_egXm7iwR0isCt_UxcGtheFEwLj9SNhxC5DWnAqKIc/edit=0) .\\n\\n* * *\\n\\n# Laptop Scores\\n\\nSorted by newest to oldest\\n\\n# Lenovo ThinkPad T14 Gen 7 and T16 Gen 5\\n\\n2026\\n\\n###### PROS\\n\\n* Storage and memory are readily repairable/upgradeable using industry-standard parts.\\n* The battery is easily replaced, and the keyboard replacement procedure is best-in-class.\\n* Overall very high modularity, including individually replaceable Thunderbolt ports.\\n* Lenovo provides thorough repair instructions and sells replacement parts.\\n\\n[Scorecard v2.2](https://www.ifixit.com/Wiki/Repairability_Scoring_Rubric_v2.2)\\n# MacBook Pro 14-inch (M5, 2025)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/Device/MacBook_Pro_14%22_2025_%28M5%29)\\n\\n2025\\n\\n###### PROS\\n\\n* Battery replacements are do-able (if not exactly easy).\\n* The Thunderbolt port design is highly modular and repair-friendly.\\n* Apple offers a full service manual and a good selection of replacement parts for end users.\\n\\n###### CONS\\n\\n* Storage is not removable or serviceable, the keyboard is riveted down, and pentalobe screws bar the way for all repairs.\\n\\n[Scorecard v2.2](https://www.ifixit.com/Wiki/Repairability_Scoring_Rubric_v2.2)\\n\\n# Lenovo ThinkPad P16 Gen 3\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/Device/Lenovo_ThinkPad_P16_Gen_3)\\n\\n2025\\n\\n###### PROS\\n\\n* Storage and memory are readily repairable/upgradeable using industry-standard parts.\\n* The battery is easily replaced, and the keyboard replacement procedure is best-in-class.\\n* Lenovo typically provides thorough support for P-series repairs (instructions and replacement parts).\\n\\n###### CONS\\n\\n...\\n\\n# MacBook Air 15″ (M2)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/Device/MacBook_Air_15%22_2023)\\n\\n2023\\n\\n###### PROS\\n\\n* Battery repairs are tough but do-able, and the fanless design is low-maintenance.\\n* Apple offers full repair instructions and replacement parts for end users.\\n\\n###### CONS\\n\\n* Storage is soldered, the keyboard is riveted down, and pentalobe screws bar the way for all repairs.\\n\\n[Scorecard v1.6](https://www.ifixit.com/Wiki/Repairability_Scoring_Rubric_v1.6)  \\n**[Learn More](https://www.ifixit.com/News/62674/m2-macbook-air-teardown-apple-forgot-the-heatsink)**\\n\\n# MacBook Air 13″ (M2)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/Device/Macbook_Air_M2_2022)\\n\\n2022\\n\\n###### PROS\\n\\n* Battery repairs are tough but do-able, and the fanless design is low-maintenance.\\n* Apple offers full repair instructions and replacement parts for end users.\\n\\n###### CONS\\n\\n* Storage is soldered, the keyboard is riveted down, and pentalobe screws bar the way for all repairs.\\n\\n[Scorecard v1.6](https://www.ifixit.\\n\\n...\\n\\nifixit.com/Wiki/Repairability_Scoring_Rubric_v1.3)  \\n**[Learn More](https://www.ifixit.com/News/54122/macbook-pro-2021-teardown)**\\n\\n[View Legacy Scores](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/legacy-laptop-scores)\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/Device/HP_Pavilion_15\",\n      \"title\": \"HP Pavilion 15 Series Repair Help: Learn How to Fix It Yourself. - iFixit\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Free Shipping on Domestic Orders $75+\\n\\nHP Pavilion 15 Series\\n\\nTable of Contents\\n\\n* Background\\n* Identification\\n* Additional Information\\n\\n* Edit\\n* Options\\n\\n* History\\n* \\n* Show Other Languages\\n\\nHP Pavilion 15 Series\\n\\n# HP Pavilion 15 Series Repair\\n\\nDevice repair and information for HP's line of Pavilion 15\\\" laptop computers.\\n\\nAuthor: Jeff Stephens (and 7 other contributors)\\n\\nCreate a Guide\\n\\n## Popular Forum Questions\\n\\nAsk a Question\\n\\n|3 Answers\\n\\n10 Score |### How to solve 5 long and 3 short caps lock blink? and not turning on. It shows 5 long and 3 short caps lock blink error....\\\")\\n\\nHP Pavilion 15 Series |\\n| --- | --- |\\n|2 Answers\\n\\n0 Score |### HP Pavilion 15 -- Verification of flashed BIOS image failed bootloop\\n\\nHP Pavilion 15 Series |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n2 Score |### re-attaching a bezel to laptop screen\\n\\nHP Pavilion 15 Series |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### Bios update corrupted but I try to recover it but its not working\\n\\nHP Pavilion 15-cc561st |\\n\\n## Background\\nHP Pavilion computers have existed since 1995. They generally compete with similar lines from Toshiba and Acer. For many people, 15 inch laptops hit the ‘Goldilocks zone’ of laptops. They’re not too big or small, and they have enough space for a good processor without sacrificing portability. These laptops are popular with content creators and professionals who need to be productive and do occasional creative tasks, but also want a reasonably portable laptop.\\n\\n## Identification\\n\\nMost HP Pavilion 15 model numbers begin with 15-, and use 15.6\\\" screens. To find your exact model of HP Pavilion 15, look for the serial number and/or the model or product number. This is often on the bottom or side of the laptop, or in the battery compartment if it is removable.\\n\\nThis [HP page](https://www.hp.com/us-en/shop/tech-takes/how-to-find-hp-laptop-model-number) explains in more detail how to find these identifying numbers. You can enter these numbers into the [HP support website](https://www.\\nsupport.hp.com/us-en) for troubleshooting and specifications.\\n\\nThis category contains device pages that can assist with troubleshooting and repair for the following models of HP Pavilion 15 laptop computers:\\n\\n* HP Pavilion 15 cs0xxx\\n* HP Pavilion 15-ab\\n* HP Pavilion 15-au\\n* HP Pavilion 15-au123cl\\n* HP Pavilion 15-aw\\n* HP Pavilion 15-ay041wm\\n* HP Pavilion 15-B\\n* HP Pavilion 15-ba003ds\\n* HP Pavilion 15-ca2073cl\\n* HP Pavilion 15-cc023cl\\n* HP Pavilion 15-cc123cl\\n* HP Pavilion 15-d017cl\\n* HP Pavilion 15-d035dx\\n* HP Pavilion 15-n232nr\\n* HP Pavilion 15-p\\n* HP Pavilion 15-p046nr\\n* HP Pavilion 15-214dx\\n* HP Pavilion 15t\\n* HP Pavilion 15z\\n* HP Pavilion TouchSmart 15\\n* HP Pavilion x360 15-bk152nr\\n\\n## Additional Information\\n\\n[HP Pavilion 15 Official Website](https://store.hp.com/us/en/mdp/pavilion-15-344522--1#!&tab=vao)\\n\\n[HP Pavilion - Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HP_Pavilion_\\\\(computer\\\\))\\n\\n[Why Use a 15 Inch Laptop?](https://www.techradar.com/uk/news/best-15-inch-laptop)\\n\\n### Author\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.cultofmac.com/ifixit-teardown\",\n      \"title\": \"iFixit Teardown | Cult of Mac\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"com/iphone-air) surprised repair experts by proving ultra-thin doesn’t have to mean harder to fix. Despite measuring just 5.6mm thick — making it Apple’s thinnest iPhone ever — the device earned a solid 7 out of 10 repairability score from iFixit in its iPhone Air teardown, matching the iPhone 16 and 16 Pro.\\n\\nAnd the teardown reveals how they made it so thin in the first place.\\n\\n[Continue reading](https://www.cultofmac.com/news/iphone-air-teardown)\\n\\n[](https://www.cultofmac.com/news/iphone-air-teardown \\\"iPhone Air teardown reveals skinny handset’s clever secrets - Comments\\\")\\n\\n[Add as a preferred source on Google](https://www.google.com/preferences/source?q=https://www.cultofmac.com)\\n\\n[## iPhone 13 series increases battery sizes by up to 18%](https://www.cultofmac.com/news/iphone-13-series-increases-battery-sizes-by-up-to-18)\\n\\nBy [Ed Hardy](https://www.cultofmac.com/author/ed-hardy \\\"Posts by Ed Hardy\\\") • 9:34 am, September 26, 2021\\n\\n* [News](https://www.cultofmac.\\n\\n...\\n\\ngoogle.com/preferences/source?q=https://www.cultofmac.com)\\n\\n[## How iFixit made its incredible iPhone 7 teardown [Kahney’s Korner podcast]](https://www.cultofmac.com/news/kyle-wiens-ifixit-iphone-7-teardown)\\n\\nBy [Leander Kahney](https://www.cultofmac.com/author/leander-kahney \\\"Posts by Leander Kahney\\\") • 1:06 pm, September 19, 2016\\n\\n* [News](https://www.cultofmac.com/news \\\"News\\\")\\n\\n[Kyle Wiens, CEO iFixit](https://www.cultofmac.com/news/kyle-wiens-ifixit-iphone-7-teardown) Thanks mostly to Kyle Wiens of iFixit, iPhone teardowns have become a tech culture phenomenon.  \\n_Photo: iFixit_\\n\\niFixit’s [iPhone 7 teardown](https://www.cultofmac.com/445749/iphone-7-plus-teardown-confirms-bigger-2900-mah-battery/) involved 30 people in three countries, an X-ray machine and lots of sleepless nights. Thanks to iFixit’s hard work, iPhone teardowns have become a tech-culture phenomenon. Millions of fans eagerly await details of the internal components of Apple’s latest devices.\\nA lot of this has to do with Kyle Wiens, CEO of [iFixit](https://www.ifixit.com/) , the second-biggest supplier of Apple parts after Apple itself, and publisher of the huge and amazing [iFixit repair wiki](https://www.ifixit.com/Guide) .\\n\\nIn this week’s episode of _Kahney’s Korner_ , I talk with Wiens about all the work that goes into making the iFixit teardowns for a massive global audience, and the hardware secrets of the iPhone 7.\\n\\n[Continue reading](https://www.cultofmac.com/news/kyle-wiens-ifixit-iphone-7-teardown)\\n\\n[](https://www.cultofmac.com/news/kyle-wiens-ifixit-iphone-7-teardown \\\"How iFixit made its incredible iPhone 7 teardown [Kahney’s Korner podcast] - Comments\\\")\\n\\n[Add as a preferred source on Google](https://www.google.com/preferences/source?q=https://www.cultofmac.com)\\n\\n[## You think Apple’s Smart Battery Case is ugly? Wait ’til you see its insides](https://www.cultofmac.com/news/you-think-apples-smart-battery-case-is-ugly-wait-til-you-see-its-insides)\\nBy [David Pierini](https://www.cultofmac.com/author/david-pierini \\\"Posts by David Pierini\\\") • 9:19 am, December 10, 2015\\n\\n* [News](https://www.cultofmac.com/news \\\"News\\\")\\n\\n[It's what's inside that counts.](https://www.cultofmac.com/news/you-think-apples-smart-battery-case-is-ugly-wait-til-you-see-its-insides) It's what's inside that counts.  \\n_Photo: iFixit_\\n\\nFor the Apple fans disappointed in the Quasimodo look of the new Smart Battery Case, there is probably great satisfaction in seeing it all busted up. Yes, the staff at _iFixit_ wasted no time prying one open to behold the guts of the beast.\\n\\n_iFixit_ did not defend the case from the “ugly” tag so many people gave it in its’ first 24 hours of public life. The technicians were impressed with the ducting on the case, which turned a downward-facing speaker into one that faces forward. The microphone also faces forward and iFixit wonders if this a preview on future designs.\\n\\n[Continue reading](https://www.cultofmac.\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/en-gb/Parts/HP_OMEN_15-dc0000\",\n      \"title\": \"HP OMEN 15-dc0000 Series Parts | iFixit\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Free delivery on orders over £65\\\\*\\n\\n1. HP OMEN 15-dc0000 Series Parts\\n2. HP OMEN 15 Series\\n3. HP OMEN Series\\n4. HP Laptop\\n5. PC Laptop\\n6. PC\\n7. All Parts\\n8. Store\\n\\nParts [Guides](https://www.ifixit.com/Device/HP_OMEN_15-dc0000) [Answers](https://www.ifixit.com/Answers/Device/HP_OMEN_15-dc0000)\\n\\n1. HP OMEN 15-dc0000 Series Parts\\n2. HP OMEN 15 Series\\n3. HP OMEN Series\\n4. HP Laptop\\n5. PC Laptop\\n6. PC\\n7. All Parts\\n8. Store\\n\\n# HP OMEN 15-dc0000 Series Parts\\n\\n## Grab a toolkit for your HP OMEN 15-dc0000 Series and fix your broken PC laptop!\\n\\niFixit has you covered with parts, tools, and free repair guides. Repair with confidence! All of our replacement parts are tested to rigorous standards and backed by our industry-leading warranty.\\n\\n## Products\\n\\nClear all filters\\n\\n### Part or Kit\\n\\n2 results\\n\\nHP SR04XL Battery - SR04XL\\n\\n### HP SR04XL Battery - SR04XL\\n\\n19\\n\\n£74.99\\n\\nHP SR03XL Battery\\n\\n### HP SR03XL Battery\\n\\n1\\n\\n£57.99\\n\\nHP SR04XL Battery - SR04XL\\n\\n### HP SR04XL Battery - SR04XL\\nReplace a dead or malfunctioning battery compatible with an HP SR04XL battery.\\n\\nNumber of reviews: 19\\n\\n£74.99\\n\\nView\\n\\nHP SR03XL Battery\\n\\n### HP SR03XL Battery\\n\\nReplace a 4550 mAh battery compatible with HP SR03XL.\\n\\nNumber of reviews: 1\\n\\n£57.99\\n\\nView\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/repairability\",\n      \"title\": \"Repairability - iFixit\",\n      \"publish_date\": \"2026-07-04\",\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"# Repairable Products Make Good Sense\\n\\n# **Repair is good for people, the planet, and product longevity** .\\n\\n# We rate products to make it easier to buy repairable devices.\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/smartphone-repairability-scores)\\n\\n# Smartphones\\n\\n[View Scores](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/smartphone-repairability-scores)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/tablet-repairability-scores)\\n\\n# Tablets\\n\\n[View Scores](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/tablet-repairability-scores)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/laptop-repairability-scores)\\n\\n# Laptops\\n\\n[View Scores](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/laptop-repairability-scores)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/wireless-earbud-repairability-scores)\\n\\n# Wireless Earbuds\\n\\n[View Scores](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/wireless-earbud-repairability-scores)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/e-reader-repairability-scores)\\n\\n# E-readers\\n\\n[View Scores](https://www.ifixit.\\ncom/repairability/e-reader-repairability-scores)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/smartwatch-repairability-scores)\\n\\n# Smartwatches\\n\\n[View Scores](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/smartwatch-repairability-scores)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/mini-pc-repairability-scores)\\n\\n# Mini PCs\\n\\n[View Scores](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/mini-pc-repairability-scores)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/handheld-game-console-repairability-scores)\\n\\n# Handheld Game Consoles\\n\\n[View Scores](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/handheld-game-console-repairability-scores)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/wireless-headphones-repairability-scores)\\n\\n# Wireless Headphones\\n\\n[View Scores](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/wireless-headphones-repairability-scores)\\n\\n# What is Repairability?\\n\\nRepairability means making it possible—and ideally easy—to repair a product.\\nA repairable product is designed with disassembly in mind (it should be easy to take apart and put back together). It must also have parts, tools, service documentation, and software available, as well as no artificial barriers to repair such as parts pairing. Together, these aspects make up the repair ecosystem.\\n\\n[Learn More](https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/gold-standard)\\n\\n# Repairable Products Make a Difference\\n\\n# 80% choose repairable\\n\\nFrance now requires that electronics manufacturers put a repairability score at the point of sale. The vast majority of French consumers say they [would give up their favorite brand](https://news.samsung.com/fr/sondage-indice-reparabilite) for a more repairable one.\\n\\n# 92% less waste\\n\\n[Microsoft found](https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.dropbox.com/s/0s1i1m6efee7cbu/Summary%2520of%2520Sustainability%2520Benefits%2520of%2520Microsoft%2520Device%2520Repair.pdf?\\n\\n...\\n\\nSometimes manufacturers use proprietary screws, requiring drivers only available to their own repair techs—like [Apple’s pentalobe](https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.ifixit.com/News/14279/apples-diabolical-plan-to-screw-your-iphone&sa=D&source=docs&ust=1688079314464072&usg=AOvVaw1MgEO3FWV2zWj3O5mpaA-A) and [Jura’s oval](https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.jura-parts.com/Jura-Oval-Head-Repair-Tool-p/10542.htm&sa=D&source=docs&ust=1688079314464146&usg=AOvVaw0wsU2MbF6sxJAGmNEuYimd) . Sometimes designers make opening a product destructive. The original [Microsoft Surface laptop](https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.ifixit.com/Teardown/Microsoft%2BSurface%2BLaptop%2BTeardown/92915&sa=D&source=docs&ust=1688079314465147&usg=AOvVaw3zIIBR3maUwYrLX_Dpw8as) had a felt case that had to be cut open and spot welds underneath that (newer models are much better!).\\n\\n# Missing access to parts, tools, and documentation\\n\\n...\\n\\nNearly half of iPhone parts today are paired, meaning that you need special manufacturer-only software to repair them without errors. A truly repairable product doesn’t have software limitations like this.\\n\\n# There’s a better way.\\n\\niFixit is working on both sides of the table, supporting  \\nlegislation to enforce Right to Repair initiatives and help  \\n[manufacturers make repairable products](https://www.ifixit.com/services) .\\n\\n# Learn More\\n\\n* Who fixes stuff? Find out more about the [iFixit community](https://www.ifixit.com/Community) .\\n* Like documentaries? Want to hear more about planned obsolescence? Check out [The Light Bulb Conspir\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_OMEN_15-dc0000\",\n      \"title\": \"HP OMEN 15-dc0000 Series Parts | iFixit\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Free Shipping on Domestic Orders $75+\\n\\n1. HP OMEN 15-dc0000 Series Parts\\n2. HP OMEN 15 Series\\n3. HP OMEN Series\\n4. HP Laptop\\n5. PC Laptop\\n6. PC\\n7. All Parts\\n8. Store\\n\\nParts [Guides](https://www.ifixit.com/Device/HP_OMEN_15-dc0000) [Answers](https://www.ifixit.com/Answers/Device/HP_OMEN_15-dc0000)\\n\\n1. HP OMEN 15-dc0000 Series Parts\\n2. HP OMEN 15 Series\\n3. HP OMEN Series\\n4. HP Laptop\\n5. PC Laptop\\n6. PC\\n7. All Parts\\n8. Store\\n\\n# HP OMEN 15-dc0000 Series Parts\\n\\n## Grab a toolkit for your HP OMEN 15-dc0000 Series and fix your broken PC laptop!\\n\\niFixit has you covered with parts, tools, and free repair guides. Repair with confidence! All of our replacement parts are tested to rigorous standards and backed by our industry-leading warranty.\\n\\n## Products\\n\\nClear all filters\\n\\n### Item Type\\n\\nBatteries 2\\n\\nKeyboards 1\\n\\n3 results\\n\\nFilters\\n\\nHP SR04XL Battery - SR04XL\\n\\n### HP SR04XL Battery - SR04XL\\n\\n19\\n\\n$69.99\\n\\nHP SR03XL Battery\\n\\n### HP SR03XL Battery\\n\\n1\\n\\n$60.99\\n\\nLifetime Guarantee\\nHP Omen 15-dc Keyboard - L32770-001\\n\\n### HP Omen 15-dc Keyboard - L32770-001\\n\\n$49.99\\n\\nHP SR04XL Battery - SR04XL\\n\\n### HP SR04XL Battery - SR04XL\\n\\nReplace a dead or malfunctioning battery compatible with an HP SR04XL battery.\\n\\nNumber of reviews: 19\\n\\n$69.99\\n\\nView\\n\\nHP SR03XL Battery\\n\\n### HP SR03XL Battery\\n\\nReplace a 4550 mAh battery compatible with HP SR03XL.\\n\\nNumber of reviews: 1\\n\\n$60.99\\n\\nView\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dc Keyboard - L32770-001\\n\\n### HP Omen 15-dc Keyboard - L32770-001\\n\\nReplace a damaged keyboard assembly compatible with HP Omen 15-dc laptops.\\n\\nLifetime Guarantee\\n\\n$49.99\\n\\nOnly 2 left in stock\\n\\nView\\n\\nStay in the loop\\n\\nLearn something new every month!\\n\\nSubscribe Let me read it first!\\n\\nApple pay.png Google pay.png Paypal.png Visa.png Mastercard.png Discover.png Amex logo Shop Pay logo\\n\\n—\\n\\n[Licensed under Creative Commons](https://www.ifixit.com/Info/Licensing)\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"warnings\": null,\n  \"usage\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"sku_search\",\n      \"count\": 1\n    }\n  ],\n  \"session_id\": \"ses_0d4353dbfffetaEyYriMe0RXin\"\n}",
